@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<MudText Typo="Typo.h6">
    Welcome to a quick and dirty way to keep track of scores on the go. This site allows you to add players, then
    track scores for those players in a variety of games.  This is designed to be lightweight and quick to use.
    It does NOT keep track of stats, players, or games across browser sessions.
</MudText>

<MudText Typo="Typo.body1">
    It does use the local browser storage to maintain state to avoid accidentally losing the current session game
    data.
</MudText>
